===Noun===
{{en-noun|sg=[[martial]] [[art]]}}

# Any of several fighting styles which contain methods of training for unarmed and armed combat; usually practiced as a sport, such as [[boxing]], [[karate]], [[judo]], [[wrestling]], or [[muay thai]]. Included in this are infantry maneuver, aerial combat, and so on.

